About Us
Since 1992, we have been serving awesome food to our Jacksonville community. We pride ourselves and making 99% of the our menu items
IN-HOUSE! Our ranch, honey mustard, pasta salad, soups, and salsa are just a few of our house favorites. Our menu is loaded with a variety of options including vegan, vegetarian, and a separate kids menu.
Though we're not just known for our great food!
We have 20 beers on tap, TONS of bottled beer and a wine menu.
We have a laid back vibe located on Big Fishweir Creek.
Whether you're here to watch the game, play a game of pool,
listen to live music, play the juke box, participate in trivia or JUST EAT!
However you wanna celebrate we'll be here for you with our quality homemade food and family friendly atmosphere!
#FamilyOwned #FamilyRun #EatDrinkLocal #HarpsRiverside #Hipstoric
Well-behaved, well-trained, leashed dogs, are allowed on our deck!
MUST have a leash that is no longer than 8 ft (Per Jax leash laws. That means no retractable leashes longer than 8 feet) AND absolutely no leaving your dogs alone at any time.
Since we are a restaurant dogs are not allowed to eat nor drink from our tables and dogs are not allowed to sit in our chairs.
DCPS EMPLOYEE DEAL
Duval county public school employees get 10% off every day at Harps!! Whether you’re here to watch the game, play a game of pool, listen to live music, play the juke box, participate in trivia or JUST EAT!
